snippet.textDisplay: This song hit me different than the others. I went through a lot as a kid, and even though people knew about it they never did anything. I still have nightmares to this day where I’m getting hurt and everyone around me doesn’t care. But through all of this I have my sister. And she was always there and always able to console me. The line, “and you say: as long as I’m here, no one can hurt you,” makes me cry while typing this because I know no matter what she’ll never let me get hurt again. This has become our song, and we quietly sing it to each other. Billie was really able to put my fears into a hauntingly beautiful song. Even thought that’s not what she meant by it, my interpretation hits too close to home. I love her. ❤️

snippet.textDisplay: The first time I listened to this song I almost started crying, I’ve been so low I’ve never saw a way out other than ending it. I went to the hospital and now I go to therapy. This triggered my ptsd and made me feel like I was in the place again. Instead of stopping the song I kept listening and it made me feel better about what happened to me. Thank you billie, my bipolar depression will never be cured but you are one of my crutches to deal with it day to day. So, thank you from the bottom of my heart ❤️

snippet.textDisplay: Man, simply, when I listened to this song, I didn't know if I screamed or cried, because it represented my life, once I screamed that I was going to kill myself, and no one called, only my brother who supported me and said, " Brother, you don't deserve this, you'll only live once with all of us who love you, so stop being a muggle, and come give me a hug! " That hug, was the only hug I got, and I felt it was someone who worried about me, man for 10 years now I have this fucking depression, and if you do not have, seriously do not lie that has only to gain attention , because you don't know what we are going through, and if you know, you know little! Well, all of Billie's songs soothe me, and make me happy, and I just want to say that: * You're a special person, if you have depression, or you don't like yourself, don't cry, don't lose your life, don't get hurt, look for someone around who loves you, that this you will forget, and only good things will remember * Bro, enjoy your life ... Cause it could be your last chance ✌🇺🇸
